  "narrative": "<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Short impact summary</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">\"Documenting Ancient Sagalassos,\" published by Leuven University Press in 2023, demonstrates a significant scholarly effort focused on the archaeological site of Sagalassos. Its commercial availability on platforms like Amazon and Goodreads suggests an intention to reach both academic and broader communities, facilitating access to this important research output.</p>\n<h3 class=\"story-subheading\">Full narrative</h3>\n<p class=\"story-text\">The book \"Documenting Ancient Sagalassos\" stands as a foundational research output within the field of archaeology, specifically addressing the significance of the ancient city of Sagalassos. Published by Leuven University Press in 2023, it illustrates a rigorous scholarly approach to understanding the site's historical context and cultural importance. The authors' commitment to making their work accessible is underscored by its presence on commercial platforms like Amazon and Goodreads, indicating an effort to engage both academic and public audiences.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">While the current citation count and online community discussions are at zero, the book is positioned to contribute to future academic discussions and possibly stimulate interest among researchers and the general public alike. The absence of citations at this stage could reflect its recent publication and the time needed for academic uptake. However, the potential for scholarly engagement remains high as the book is integrated into coursework and reference materials over time.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">This work has not yet accrued notable mentions on platforms like Wikipedia or Reddit, indicating the need for further dissemination to foster community discourse. As it stands, \"Documenting Ancient Sagalassos\" has the potential to influence future archaeological research and public understanding of ancient urban environments as it gains visibility in academic circles.</p>\n<p class=\"story-text\">Overall, the narrative surrounding \"Documenting Ancient Sagalassos\" is characterized by its exploration of significant archaeological themes, and it is expected to grow in relevance as it garners attention and citations in the coming years. The scholarly community's response will ultimately shape the book's impact within its discipline and beyond.</p>",
